00:06:07.865 --> 00:06:13.415
Why do we do it to commemorate history,
promote causes and foster unity.

00:06:13.655 --> 00:06:16.865
When are they observed
annually on fixed dates.

00:06:17.375 --> 00:06:22.505
Where either globally like uns or
nationally within a country who

00:06:22.745 --> 00:06:28.055
governments big organizations like
the UN and WHO, NGOs, and of course

00:06:28.055 --> 00:06:32.975
people like us, and how is it done
through events, campaigns, educational

00:06:32.975 --> 00:06:37.715
programs, and all sorts of public
