00:06:37.895 --> 00:06:39.755
Example, one Question.

00:06:40.025 --> 00:06:43.340
World Environment Day is
celebrated annually on which date?

00:06:43.845 --> 00:06:49.545
A June 1st, B June 5th, C
July 11th, D August 12th.

00:06:49.845 --> 00:06:51.345
Understand the question before.

00:06:51.345 --> 00:06:52.605
Moving to explanation.

00:06:52.995 --> 00:06:56.235
The question is a straightforward
one, asking for the date

00:06:56.235 --> 00:06:57.585
of World Environment Day.

00:06:58.005 --> 00:07:01.575
World Environment Day is a major
global event for environmental

00:07:01.575 --> 00:07:02.835
awareness and action.

00:07:03.159 --> 00:07:05.650
It is celebrated every year on June 5th.

00:07:06.070 --> 00:07:09.700
Looking at the options, option
B matches our answer perfectly.

00:07:09.940 --> 00:07:12.550
Answer Option B, example two.

00:07:12.760 --> 00:07:13.330
Question.

00:07:13.599 --> 00:07:16.479
International yoga day is
observed on which date?

00:07:16.690 --> 00:07:18.130
A June 15th.

00:07:18.280 --> 00:07:22.585
B June 21st, C July 1st, D July 15th.

00:07:22.585 --> 00:07:25.575
Understand the question
before moving to explanation.

00:07:26.200 --> 00:07:29.200
This one asks for the date
of International Yoga Day.

00:07:29.530 --> 00:07:34.060
You need to recall the date that promotes
the wonderful benefits of yoga worldwide.

00:07:34.479 --> 00:07:37.810
International Yoga Day is
celebrated on June 21st.

00:07:38.140 --> 00:07:42.460
Fun fact, this date was chosen because
it's the summer solstice in the Northern

00:07:42.460 --> 00:07:44.500
Hemisphere, the longest day of the year.

00:07:44.825 --> 00:07:49.895
So matching this with the options B is
the correct choice, answer option B.

00:07:50.075 --> 00:07:54.905
Example three question on which date
is National Voters Day celebrated

00:07:54.905 --> 00:08:01.865
in India, A January 12th, B January
25th, C, February 28th, D March 8th.

00:08:02.224 --> 00:08:04.895
Understand the question
before moving to explanation.

00:08:05.315 --> 00:08:08.135
The question specifically
asks For a National Day in

00:08:08.135 --> 00:08:09.530
India, national Voters Day.

00:08:10.380 --> 00:08:14.940
The day was established to encourage young
voters to participate in our democracy.

00:08:15.359 --> 00:08:17.430
You need to recall this specific date.

00:08:17.820 --> 00:08:22.710
National Voters Day is celebrated on
January 25th each year because this

00:08:22.710 --> 00:08:26.760
was the day the Election Commission
of India was founded back in 1950.

00:08:27.180 --> 00:08:31.260
Comparing this with the options
provided, option B is the correct answer.

00:08:31.469 --> 00:08:33.539
Answer option B. Thank you.

